- UX: Tightened right-side label padding to match the smaller toggle and avoid excessive spacing.


###2026.03.19.17
- Fix: Corrected Compact Matrix CSS scoping so only top-level dashboard cards are affected.
- Fix: Switched Compact Matrix to a stable top-level grid container to prevent layout breakage in Dashboard and nested folder views.
- Regression guard: Kept dashboard layout contracts and responsive behavior checks passing after the selector fix.


###2026.03.19.16
- Feature: Added `Compact Matrix` as a new dashboard widget layout mode for Docker and VM views.
- UX: Compact Matrix now renders folders as a denser card grid with responsive 3-column desktop, 2-column tablet, and 1-column phone behavior.
- Compatibility: Updated dashboard layout normalization across settings runtime, shared utils, and server prefs validation to persist `compactmatrix` safely.


###2026.03.19.15
