###2026.03.19.04
- Quality: Docker/VM/Dashboard runtimes now coalesce rapid refresh calls and queue folder renders to prevent overlapping redraw churn.
- UX: Performance mode now applies a stricter minimum live-refresh cadence and reduced-motion runtime styling.
- Quality: Performance mode restores only a capped number of expanded branches on large nested trees to keep render cost predictable.


###2026.03.19.03
- UX: Folder editor now enforces duplicate-name checks by parent path (sibling scope) and suggests the next available name.
- UX: New child folder creation now inherits smart defaults from the selected parent (icon/preview/color) unless the field was manually edited.
- Quality: Nested tree integrity scans now include depth warnings and empty-branch detection in addition to orphan/cycle checks.
- Quality: Import preview/apply now supports nested path-based ID mapping so matching parent/name paths update existing folders instead of duplicating.
- Fix: Import diff now reports parent-path changes explicitly, and import summaries surface path-collision resolver notes.


###2026.03.19.02
