- UX: Added Basic/Advanced modes (Basic default), quick presets (Recent/Favorites/Most used/Folder icons), and clearer Scope/Pack labels.
- UX: Replaced floating pack actions with an inline Pack actions dropdown panel to keep controls anchored and easier to understand.
- UX: Added active filter badges plus one-click "Clear all filters" to recover quickly when results are empty.
- Fix: Added clearer empty-state guidance and step hints so users know exactly what to do next.


