###2026.03.18.10
- Fix: Added lightweight direct-member row recovery in Docker nested parent expansion so parent containers remain visible when expanded.
- Fix: Collapse/expand and folder autostart now use the same direct-member resolver to avoid class-drift desync after import/reload.
- Test: Hardened nested expansion contract checks for the direct-member resolver path.


###2026.03.18.09
- Fix: Docker nested parent expansion now resolves direct-member rows from folder membership (not only CSS classes), preventing blank parent rows and missing direct containers.
- Fix: Hardened collapse/expand/autostart flows to recover direct container rows by canonical container ID when class tags drift.
- Test: Added regression guards for the direct-member row recovery path in nested folder expansion.


###2026.03.18.08
- Fix: Restored mobile settings overflow (3-dot) button size to 24px while preserving touch-safe spacing.
- Fix: Repositioned quick-actions popup to iPhone safe-area bounds so right-edge and bottom clipping are prevented.
- Fix: Added strong tree-toggle button reset styles to stop lingering mobile settings box artifacts.


###2026.03.18.07
- Fix: Restored mobile settings overflow (3-dot) button size to 24px while keeping touch-safe spacing.
- Fix: Anchored row quick-actions modal to iPhone safe-area bounds so it no longer clips on the side or bottom.
- Fix: Added hard reset styles for tree toggle buttons to stop inherited mobile theme box artifacts in settings rows.


###2026.03.18.06
- UX: Refined settings and on-screen update messaging for clarity and consistency.
